text:
Updates from @DOHgovph this 28 May:

There are 539 people newly confirmed with #COVID19PH. The total confirmed cases in Philippines are now 15,588.

92 more people with COVID-19 have recovered, bringing the total recoveries to 3,598. https://t.co/JixRnNVs8l
